passes.title: Saga middleware – it should handle loadOpportunities error
Opportunity component – it should render the correct values for the fields
Opportunity component – it should render all the week maps as "none" if there are no timelines
Opportunity component – it should render week maps with proper dates if there are production timelines
Range Picker – it should mount properly
Range Picker – it should not display label if we don't know what it is
Range Picker – it should call the callback when changing the from date
Range Picker – it should call the callback when changing the to date
somethingBeingTestedList – it should render the somethingBeingTestedList headers if there are props loaded
somethingBeingTestedList – it should not render the somethingBeingTestedList if there are no props loaded
Wrapper – it should mount properly
Wrapper – it should properly parse the state
Wrapper – it should render the wrapper header with the 5 links
Wrapper – it should display the correct active link
Wrapper – it should dispatch "setOpportunitiesFilter" when clicking onClickSort
Wrapper – it should handle dispatch
Wrapper – it should properly order the opportunities descending
Wrapper – it should properly order the opportunities ascending
WeekMap – it should render the week map
Loader – it should render the loader
Sort Opportunities Reducer – it should return initial state
Sort Opportunities Reducer – it should handle sorting by filter type and order
Opportunities Reducer – it should return initial state
Opportunities Reducer – it should handle the loaded opportunities
Actions – it should create an action to set opportunities filter
Detail modal component – it should render the detail modal link
Detail modal component – it should have a closed state
Detail modal component – it should change state to open after clicking on the link
Detail modal component – it should change state to closed after clicking on the close button
